on 11/19/2011 @ around 7:10 pm I was at Mehek waiting to be seated. When I nicely asked them if I could take a place that I thought would be a little quite, the person starting yelling and arguing and said "I am busy - you have to take the place i give" - I was shocked to see the treatment and requested if i could speak to manager, the reply came " i am the manager" - I didnt want to spoil my evening, I walked out......
